CPP-Package-Starter version 0.0.3
================================
 INSTALL
================================

Perl Makefile.PL
make
make install

================================
 USAGE
================================
cpppackage --project MyProject --author example@example.org

cd ./MyProject
./scripts/genclass --name MyClass1
./scripts/genclass --name MyClass2 --fixture
./scripts/genclass --name MyHeaderOnlyClass --nosource

... and edit class and tests


./scripts/build


./scripts/clean


# If you develop on MacOS, you can build Xcode project template

./scripts/xcode
open ./xcode/MyProject.xcodeproj


